race.description: Mark Gurry & Associates Maiden Mobile Pace
race.comment: SINKRATE (1) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 4 metres from the winner in third over 1780m at Redcliffe. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Meets a similar line up and he can take this out. HEZ OUR PLAYBOY (5) drew wide last start and was easily accounted for, beaten 13 metres into fifth at this track over 1850m. Won't find this any harder and from this more favourable draw he can turn the recent result around. TAKING STOCK (3) could only manage fifth first-up two runs ago then broke in the run and finished a long last at the latest appearance over 1780m at Redcliffe. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Only needs to get things right to be in the money. ALONG THE WAY (7) is in the mix following a sixth at her most recent appearance over 1780m at Redcliffe.
